# <strong>config -s /usr/src/sys -b . SOMEFILE</strong>
</pre>
nastêpnie jeden z nastêpuj±cych:

<pre>
    # <strong>make depend</strong>
         <b><i>- LUB -</i></b>
    # <strong>make clean && make depend</strong>
